##########################################################################
# README_s
# To simulate the effects of atmospheric turbulence 
#
# See complementary documentation in "s_source.txt"
# 
# JLP
# Version 09/06/2006
##########################################################################

s_source.txt
s_pscorg.for : simulation of phase screen (from Tadashi Nakajima, 1988)
               original version with fourn1 
               
s_screen.for : modified version of s_pscorg.for by JLP, with fft_2d

s_psc.for : modified version of s_psorg by Marco de Vos, with four2

# Library 
s_fourn1.for : Fourier transform fourn1 from Num. Recipees 
           modified by Marco de Vos. This version is called "four2" 
           and should be used with s_psc.for

